  "text": "Despite relatively innocuous cytology, the disease is highly aggressive with an almost constant fatal outcome and a median overall survival barely exceeding one year [CITATION_1] . Occasional long survivors have been reported and few patients respond to cytarabine or deoxycoformycin [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] .",
